channel.title: Make a song out of this!
channel.description:
A bit of a while ago, I was on Auxy, and at the same time I was on my piano keyboard, when suddenly this beat popped into mind.
I couldn’t come up with anything to add, so I decided to not let it go to waste and see what you guys can come up with!
